<<declare $playerName = "Player">>

Narrator: A woman maybe around her twenties to early thirties enters the room. She has a [i]nasty[/i] scar on her left eye.
Officer: Mornin’, {$playerName}. I’m Officer Sarah Blakesley, your supervisor. 
Narrator: You expected her to extend her hand to you, but instead they were kept perfectly positioned behind her back. 
-> Good morning - Ma’am. 
Officer: Right then, I believe you know what to do to ‘elp out good folks in need? 
Officer: You ain’t got the foggiest? It’s alright. Tell you what, I’ll be your first customer. I promise you it’ll be as easy as pie. 
Officer: Ahem. Good mornin’. Look here, I have a long shift comin’ up soon and I’ll be completely knackered before long. You reckon you’ve got something - anythin’ that can ‘elp me with that?
Officer: (hint:  there’s a handy recipe book on the bo’om left side of the screen)
<<show_book>>
<<wait_for_book>>
